{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:18:11.435153+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: a92a3a4b2ea3eaf6bb79b3123db671fd5c661936)", "id": "lc_6bc44d77-f3dd-4aa0-8b82-65bad1a8ccc6"}, {"type": "text", "text": "version: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  web:\n    build: .\n    command: python main.py\n    volumes:\n      - ./:/usr/src/app/\n    ports:\n      - 11000:11000\n    env_file:\n      - ./.env\n    depends_on:\n      - postgres\n      - redis\n  postgres:\n    image: postgres\n    ports:\n      - 5432:5432\n    env_file:\n      - ./.env\n  redis:\n    image: redis:alpine\n    ports:\n      - 6379:6379\n    env_file:\n      - ./.env", "id": "lc_e782ffd2-a004-43d5-b1d5-8cb871f3b844"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "d1cd49d1-209e-4c9a-b2a6-079e0cafa279", "tool_call_id": "call_e3042529789d4aa09f140d61", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:18:22.128277+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's the full picture of the dependency and service stack for this FastAPI template:\n\n---\n\n## **Python Dependencies** (from `Pipfile`)\n\n| Category | Package | Details |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Web Framework** | `fastapi[all]` | FastAPI with all optional extras (includes Uvicorn, Pydantic, etc.) |\n| **Database** | `databases[postgresql]` | Async database abstraction layer (PostgreSQL variant) |\n| | `asyncpg` | Async PostgreSQL driver |\n| | `psycopg2` | Sync PostgreSQL driver (used by Alembic migrations) |\n| | `alembic` | Database migration tool (SQLAlchemy-based) |\n| | `sqlalchemy-utils` | SQLAlchemy utility helpers |\n| **Auth** | `python-jose[cryptography]` | JOSE/JWT token creation & verification |\n| | `passlib[bcrypt]` | Password hashing with bcrypt |\n| | `python-multipart` | Required for OAuth2 form-based login (`username`/`password`) |\n| **Redis** | `aioredis` | Async Redis client |\n| **Testing** | `pytest` | Test runner |\n\n---\n\n## **Service Stack** (from `docker-compose.yml`)\n\n| Service | Image / Runtime | Port |\n|---|---|---|\n| **web** | Custom Dockerfile (Python 3.9, runs `main.py`) | `11000` |\n| **postgres** | Official `postgres` image | `5432` |\n| **redis** | `redis:alpine` | `6379` |\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n- **Database:** **PostgreSQL**, accessed asynchronously via `asyncpg` + the `databases` library, with `psycopg2` available for synchronous Alembic migrations. `sqlalchemy-utils` provides extra ORM helpers.\n- **Auth:** **JWT-based authentication** using `python-jose` for token signing/verification and `passlib[bcrypt]` for password hashing. `python-multipart` enables FastAPI's built-in OAuth2 password-flow form parsing.\n- **Redis:** Supported via the **`aioredis`** async client (likely used for caching, session storage, or rate limiting).\n- **Overall architecture:** A containerized FastAPI app backed by PostgreSQL and Redis, with Alembic for database migrations.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 535, "prompt_tokens": 3791, "total_tokens": 4326, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 32, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 3520, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000596007, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000130557, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00046545}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863491-NLOie7QUtT2hlcsV4Ovk", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3bc-5d6b-7ae0-90dc-c8b124f30564-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 3791, "output_tokens": 535, "total_tokens": 4326, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 3520}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 32}}}}]}}}
